details.alternate_methods:
You can pick up passport application forms from your [local Post Office.](http://www.postoffice.co.uk/branch-finder "Find a Post Office"){:rel="external"} 

You can also [request a passport application form to be sent to you in the post.](https://forms.direct.gov.uk/forms/form/4/en/request_a_passport_application_form_to_be_sent_to_you_in_the_post "Request a passport application form to be sent to you in the post"){:rel="external"}

*[IPS]: Identity and Passport Service
